{
  "title": "ABAP Query creation for Functional Consultant",
  "content": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">Introduction:<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\nline-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">In Projects, sometimes based\non user requirement we may need to develop customized report. But in few cases\nrequirement can be fulfilled by creating ABAP queries with the minimal\ntechnical knowledge by the Functional Consultant.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">Reporting\noptions in SAP:<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:Wingdings;mso-fareast-font-family:\nWingdings;mso-bidi-font-family:Wingdings\">Ø<span style=\"font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">SAP\nprovided reports<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:Wingdings;mso-fareast-font-family:\nWingdings;mso-bidi-font-family:Wingdings\">Ø<span style=\"font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">Custom\ncoded reports (ABAP)<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:Wingdings;mso-fareast-font-family:\nWingdings;mso-bidi-font-family:Wingdings\">Ø<span style=\"font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">SAP\nQuery or ABAP Query<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:Wingdings;mso-fareast-font-family:\nWingdings;mso-bidi-font-family:Wingdings\">Ø<span style=\"font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">Quick\nViewer – Transaction SQVI – single use query<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:Wingdings;mso-fareast-font-family:\nWingdings;mso-bidi-font-family:Wingdings\">Ø<span style=\"font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">Module\nspecific Information Systems – LIS, Report Painter,<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:Wingdings;mso-fareast-font-family:\nWingdings;mso-bidi-font-family:Wingdings\">Ø<span style=\"font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">Report\nWriter, PMIS, SIS<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:Wingdings;mso-fareast-font-family:\nWingdings;mso-bidi-font-family:Wingdings\">Ø<span style=\"font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">Third\nParty<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:Wingdings;mso-fareast-font-family:\nWingdings;mso-bidi-font-family:Wingdings\">Ø<span style=\"font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">Business\nWarehouse/Business Objects<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">ABAP\nQuery:-<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\nline-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">ABAP Query or SAP Query is a\nfunctional tool used to develop simple report creating queries instead of\nwriting ABAP report program. Can create Query from one or more tables. Using\nSAP templates, we need to just add the tables for the required fields in the\nreport and creating join condition to link those tables and to pull the data\nfor the respective fields.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:\n&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">Before using, check if SAP standard reports might already\nmeet your requirements.<o:p></o:p></span></p>",
